ng Huyền Quang tôn giả - 贈玄光尊者</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Minh-T%C3%B4ng/author-4trx3YJ-cefKhX0g_XM7Sw">Trần Minh Tông</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/U%C3%B4ng-Nguy%C3%AAn-L%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng/Thu%E1%BB%B7-long-ng%C3%A2m-Ho%C3%A0i-h%C3%A0-chu-trung-d%E1%BA%A1-v%C4%83n-cung-nh%C3%A2n-c%E1%BA%A7m-thanh/poem-7702DGpcVjSVO8xQg8V_fQ">Thuỷ long ngâm - Hoài hà chu trung dạ văn cung nhân cầm thanh - 水龍吟－</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/U%C3%B4ng-Nguy%C3%AAn-L%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng/author-HbKyCtS3WFreEebdROalkQ">Uông Nguyên Lượng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-M%E1%BA%A1nh-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%99i-xu%E1%BA%A5t/poem-SURrVypCme4I6f33jiLrgA">Tội xuất - 罪出</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-M%E1%BA%A1nh-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-M_NlL2QYyIpgu5vZrvAs8w">Triệu Mạnh Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-Ch%E1%BA%A9n/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-V%C5%A9-H%E1%BA%A7u/poem-mJINZ6IW4mVT1B_S4Co--Q">Vịnh Vũ Hầu - 詠武侯</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-Ch%E1%BA%A9n/author-bMSP5YOXWyK1jTzTI9MKNQ">Nguyên Chẩn</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
